        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>行人重识别资源整理</title>
      <link href="/2019/02/09/%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%BA%E9%87%8D%E8%AF%86%E5%88%AB%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E6%95%B4%E7%90%86/"/>
      <url>/2019/02/09/%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%BA%E9%87%8D%E8%AF%86%E5%88%AB%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E6%95%B4%E7%90%86/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>近期所做的本科毕业设计是基于深度学习的行人重识别，从2019年1月份正式开始进入这个课题，陆续阅读了几十篇这个领域的论文，阅读了几个写的很棒的代码库，做了不多的实验，觉得很有必要按照该领域的不同研究方法对论文进行整理归纳，也希望能维护一个<code>LeaderBoard</code>,对<code>BaseLine</code>,<code>State of the art</code>进行更新，也方便下学期英文论文的写作和对比试验的展开。我也会进行重识别领域主流数据集、开源代码的解读等工作。<br><a id="more"></a></p>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> 计算机视觉 </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> 深度学习 </tag>
            
            <tag> 行人重识别 </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>Markdown&amp;&amp;Latex语法学习</title>
      <link href="/2019/02/09/Markdown-Latex%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/"/>
      <url>/2019/02/09/Markdown-Latex%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>工欲善其事，必先利其器。对于经常需要写各种科技论文（英文/中文）以及技术博客的童鞋而言，掌握常用的<code>MarkDown、Latex</code>语法尤为重要。这篇博客讲述一些最频繁使用的<code>MarkDown、Latex</code>语法以及自身所填的一些坑。<br><a id="more"></a></p><h1 id="从Word走来"><a href="#从Word走来" class="headerlink" title="从Word走来"></a>从Word走来</h1><p>我们最开始接触的排版软件是微软出品的Office,它是一个足够强大的软件，但当涉及大量的数学公式、图表的编号和交叉引用时，Office内置的丑陋公式字体和薄弱的交叉应用功能就显得苍白无力了。<br>但大部分学校的本科毕业论文好像并不支持Latex, 所以还是有必要扯一下Office。</p><h2 id="Word"><a href="#Word" class="headerlink" title="Word"></a>Word</h2><p>对于word而言，<a href="http://www.mathtype.cn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>MathType</strong></a>是支持最好的公式编辑软件，但是MathType是收费的，而且价格昂贵。这里提供一个<a href="https://pan.baidu.com/s/1VgBaxxgDUq1RAkqw5Y-2iQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener">下载链接</a>, 提取码是:<code>7xin</code>。安装好并破解就可以永久使用了。 </p><h2 id="PPT"><a href="#PPT" class="headerlink" title="PPT"></a>PPT</h2><p>对于ppt而言，有一个比较好的开源插件支持Latex语法的使用:<a href="http://www.jonathanleroux.org/software/iguanatex/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>IguanaTex</strong></a>。它会调用Latex编译器来编译Latex代码并生成无损的图片(意味着不必担心放大十倍而模糊)甚至矢量图。它支持所有的Latex语法，所以我们可以用这个插件键入代码生成数学公式、流程图等并以ppt的形式展示。<br><img src="//hfutzzw.github.io/2019/02/09/Markdown-Latex语法学习/slide1.PNG" alt="公式"><br><img src="//hfutzzw.github.io/2019/02/09/Markdown-Latex语法学习/slide2.PNG" alt="流程图"></p><h1 id="走到Web端去"><a href="#走到Web端去" class="headerlink" title="走到Web端去"></a>走到Web端去</h1><p>在本地书写markdown语言，自动解析成html，在浏览器上渲染是写技术博客的常用做法。<br>书写markdown语言推荐使用<a href="https://code.visualstudio.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>VScode</strong></a>及其提供的MarkDown在本地实时预览的插件：<strong>Markdown Preview Enhanced</strong>。顺带说一下，开源的VScode真是神器，它在<a href="https://github.com/Microsoft/vscode" target="_blank" rel="noopener">github</a>上的star非常高。</p><h2 id="Markdown语法"><a href="#Markdown语法" class="headerlink" title="Markdown语法"></a>Markdown语法</h2><p>markdown的语法非常简单，我们只需掌握经常使用的十几个语法即可，大家自行查看。</p><h3 id="插入代码块"><a href="#插入代码块" class="headerlink" title="插入代码块"></a>插入代码块</h3><p><code>import tensorflow as tf</code><br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">from __future__ import absolute_import</span><br><span class="line">from __future__ import print_function</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">from torch.utils.data import DataLoader</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">from .dataset_loader import ImageDataset, VideoDataset</span><br><span class="line">from .datasets import init_imgreid_dataset, init_vidreid_dataset</span><br><span class="line">from .transforms import build_transforms</span><br><span class="line">from .samplers import build_train_sampler</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">class BaseDataManager(object):</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    @property</span><br><span class="line">    def num_train_pids(self):</span><br><span class="line">        return self._num_train_pids</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    @property</span><br><span class="line">    def num_train_cams(self):</span><br><span class="line">        return self._num_train_cams</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    def return_dataloaders(self):</span><br><span class="line">        &quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">        Return trainloader and testloader dictionary</span><br><span class="line">        &quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">        return self.trainloader, self.testloader_dict</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    def return_testdataset_by_name(self, name):</span><br><span class="line">        &quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">        Return query and gallery, each containing a list of (img_path, pid, camid).</span><br><span class="line">        &quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">        return self.testdataset_dict[name][&apos;query&apos;], self.testdataset_dict[name][&apos;gallery&apos;]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h3 id="插入本地-网络图片、超链接"><a href="#插入本地-网络图片、超链接" class="headerlink" title="插入本地/网络图片、超链接"></a>插入本地/网络图片、超链接</h3><p><a href="https://www.baidu.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">百度</a><br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[超链接名](超链接地址)</span><br><span class="line">[百度](https://www.baidu.com/)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><img src="http://www.hfut.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/69/b1/245c5de846fd96fa699eb5a39501/554bd2c9-13f5-4fd2-a53c-d2263184963f.jpg" alt="新年"></p><p><img src="http://www.hfut.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/69/b1/245c5de846fd96fa699eb5a39501/554bd2c9-13f5-4fd2-a53c-d2263184963f.jpg" width="500" height="150" div="" align="center"></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![图片名](图片地址)</span><br><span class="line">![新年](http://www.hfut.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/69/b1/245c5de846fd96fa699eb5a39501/554bd2c9-13f5-4fd2-a53c-d2263184963f.jpg)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><center class="half">    <img src="https://timgsa.baidu.com/timg?image&quality=80&size=b9999_10000&sec=1549698302881&di=9406db58c4c377bf3c2ab378130bd8ef&imgtype=0&src=http%3A%2F%2F06imgmini.eastday.com%2Fmobile%2F20181013%2F20181013154351_bc8a0150d1efc43e36eb8bb84817cc88_1.jpeg" width="200"><img src="https://timgsa.baidu.com/timg?image&quality=80&size=b9999_10000&sec=1549698407482&di=7b3a4f009229d7815cecf1cbf2e6cf73&imgtype=0&src=http%3A%2F%2Fi2.hdslb.com%2Fbfs%2Farchive%2F9343c6d9c03e31cfdcfb81e253a2af84b5db817d.jpg" width="200"></center><h3 id="字体渲染"><a href="#字体渲染" class="headerlink" title="字体渲染"></a>字体渲染</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">*合肥工业大学*</span><br><span class="line">**合肥工业大学**</span><br><span class="line">***合肥工业大学***</span><br><span class="line">~~合肥工业大学~~</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em>合肥工业大学</em><br><strong>合肥工业大学</strong><br><strong><em>合肥工业大学</em></strong><br><del>合肥工业大学</del></p><h3 id="列表"><a href="#列表" class="headerlink" title="列表"></a>列表</h3><blockquote><p>无序列表</p><ul><li>安徽</li><li>江苏</li><li>浙江</li></ul><p>有序列表</p><ol><li>杭州</li><li>北京</li><li>合肥</li></ol></blockquote><h3 id="插入表格"><a href="#插入表格" class="headerlink" title="插入表格"></a>插入表格</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">表头|表头|表头</span><br><span class="line">---|:--:|---:</span><br><span class="line">内容|内容|内容</span><br><span class="line">内容|内容|内容</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">第二行分割表头和内容。</span><br><span class="line">- 有一个就行，为了对齐，多加了几个</span><br><span class="line">文字默认居左</span><br><span class="line">-两边加：表示文字居中</span><br><span class="line">-右边加：表示文字居右</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="table-container"><table><thead><tr><th style="text-align:center">company</th><th style="text-align:center">base</th><th style="text-align:center">difficulty</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td style="text-align:center">SenseTime</td><td style="text-align:center">Shenzhen</td><td style="text-align:center">hard</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:center">MSRA</td><td style="text-align:center">Beijing</td><td style="text-align:center">hard</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:center">Alibaba</td><td style="text-align:center">Hangzhou</td><td style="text-align:center">medium</td></tr></tbody></table></div><h3 id="插入公式"><a href="#插入公式" class="headerlink" title="插入公式"></a>插入公式</h3><p>在浏览器端渲染公式，推荐使用<a href="https://www.mathjax.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>MathJax</strong></a>, <code>A JavaScript display engine for mathematics that works in all browsers.</code> 它与原生的Latex语法兼容，而且公式字体渲染的相当漂亮。</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\tan(x) = \frac{\sin(x)}{\cos(x)}</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">S = \sum_{i=1}^{n} \frac{1}{i+1}</script><p>\begin{align}<br>  (a + b)^3  &amp;= (a + b) (a + b)^2        \\<br>             &amp;= (a + b)(a^2 + 2ab + b^2) \\<br>             &amp;= a^3 + 3a^2b + 3ab^2 + b^3<br>\end{align}</p><p>y=\begin{cases}<br>-x,\quad x\leq 0\\<br>x, \quad x&gt;0<br>\end{cases}</p>]]></content>
      
      
